{"tid":2414880,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"洗米華進軍加密貨幣界","createTime":"2021-02-19T18:21:42.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T02:18:58.000Z","uid":44730,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"57b8a6bc9aa79d4009fa0f7a810d48c2695889e6","tid":2414880,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:21:42.000Z","msg":"人稱「洗米華」的周焯華旗下太陽國際（8029）宣佈，就收購1,000台加密貨幣礦機訂立無法律約束力的諒解備忘錄，以於不遲於3個月訂立正式協議。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/CWFH8qUxhDA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FCWFH8qUxhDA&d=VW1JDW%2BJF%2FyRlCRofLrhGnHDV1nRQV6f8GM9BbigJgY%3D&h=771f93ec\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/CWFH8qUxhDA</a><br />\n拍影片澄清資金傳聞。"},{"pid":"66e3aaeb0f64615f30b33e0b6fe7b135168b7f43","tid":2414880,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:21:52.000Z","msg":"根據諒解備忘錄，太陽國際擬收購加密貨幣採礦設備，包括合共1,000台加密貨幣礦機Bitmain Antminer S19、Bitmain Antminer T19、MicroBT Whatsminer M32及MicroBT Whatsminer M31S。賣方主要從事蒙古、新疆和四川省的加密貨幣礦場的運營提供設備。太陽國際擬按每股0.321元發行新股作為支付代價，較停牌前收市價為0.4元折讓19.8%。"},{"pid":"35f736571d96909927d7f3732f5ab67230ae56d9","tid":2414880,"uid":44730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:22:08.000Z","msg":"對於突然進軍加密貨幣界，太陽國際表示，該集團主要從事放債、證券和期貨經紀、資產管理服務及投資於配種馬，訂立上述諒解備忘錄能使集團業務發展多樣化。"},{"pid":"fb02c0a8f39cfb058fd424cfe4bc8d8be0bd04b5","tid":2414880,"uid":71237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:40:03.000Z","msg":"買RIOT MARA都唔買太陽城"},{"pid":"9399f7b29cb040e1ebf12de107abe5ad9dd59ca0","tid":2414880,"uid":11572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:41:52.000Z","msg":"佢似比人水左多D<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c28beb8c68727c63838ae1a588cf808922f9242f","tid":2414880,"uid":232493,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9399f7b29cb040e1ebf12de107abe5ad9dd59ca0","tid":2414880,"uid":11572,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-19T18:4